Recommend and rate your favorite SPA hotel now!

The Falstaff SPA Guide 2024

What makes a unique SPA hotel for you? Is it the spacious or particularly cozy spa area? Is it the exclusive treatments? Or is it the relaxing location by the water or in the mountains that lets you switch off immediately upon arrival and recharge your batteries?

In search of the best SPA hotels we ask you for your opinion! Rate your favorite hotel now and help us support other guests in their booking decision.

Each hotel is evaluated by the Falstaff community as well as by a jury of experts and specialists in 5 categories: Ambience, SPA area, treatments, sports & fitness, as well as cuisine. The individual scores result in a total of max. 100 points.

There are plenty of ways to relax and to be pampered at the SPA Guide 2024 we will then present you the best SPA Hotels of the Year in Austria, Germany, Switzerland and Northern Italy as well as international classics and insider tips.
